      "parameters": {
        "content": "### AI Chatbot Operating Guidelines\n\n- When an employee asks for a contact person, first search `company_files` for the most relevant contact.\n- If a contact is found but details such as email or phone number are missing, use `employee_lookup_tool` to retrieve the missing information.\n- If no contact is found in `company_files`:\n  1. Use `employee_lookup_tool` with `\"HR\"` or the most relevant department name to find the senior-most person in that department.\n  2. If no department contact is found, ask the employee for their name.\n  3. Use `employee_lookup_tool` to identify the employee’s supervisor.\n  4. Use `employee_lookup_tool` again to retrieve the supervisor’s contact details.\n  5. Share the supervisor’s contact information and recommend them as the best next point of contact.",
        "height": 585,
        "width": 706
      },
