    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# AI HR Policy & Benefits Chatbot\n\nThis workflow builds an internal HR assistant that answers employee questions using company policy documents and BambooHR data.\n\n## What it does\n- Pulls company policy PDFs from BambooHR\n- Splits and embeds documents for semantic search\n- Stores them in Supabase vector store\n- Lets employees ask HR questions in chat\n- Retrieves answers from handbook, benefits, 401k, and expense policies\n- Can also look up employee or department contacts from BambooHR\n\n## Use cases\n- Internal HR helpdesk\n- Employee self-service\n- Policy and benefits Q&A\n- Contact lookup for departments or managers\n\n## Notes\n- Requires BambooHR, OpenAI, and Supabase setup\n- Best for internal company knowledge bases\n- Can be extended with Slack, Teams, or website chat",
        "height": 624,
        "width": 752,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
